reviews.review_text: Do it in the road Well I had this on cassete the boys had these new songs for me at the tme any how gloria mr fantacy do it the road this is a good recordin check it out
BCT The segue between Throwing Stones and Lovelight is really really really really really  good.  First set Down on the Bottom is a Weir rarity.
